          <title>
            <string language="en">Vibrating wave pattern in a guitar</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Vibrierendes Welle Muster in einer Guitarre</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Configuration vibrante de vague dans une guitare</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Teste padrão vibrando da onda em uma guitarra</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Modello di vibrazione dell'onda in un guitar</string>

            <string language="x-mt-es">Modelo de la onda que vibra en una guitarra</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">Third of three illustrations showing the vibrations of a plucked guitar string. This illustration shows the wave pattern produced by combining the first two illustrations.</string>
          </description>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Third von drei Abbildungen, welche die 
Erschütterungen einer gezupften Guitarre Zeichenkette zeigen. 
Diese Abbildung zeigt das Welle Muster, das indem sie die ersten
zwei Abbildungen produziert wird, kombiniert.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Tiers de trois illustrations montrant les 
vibrations d'une chaîne de caractères plumée de guitare. 
Cette illustration montre la configuration de vague produite en 
combinant les deux premières illustrations.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Third de três ilustrações que mostram as 
vibrações de uma corda arrancada da guitarra. Esta 
ilustração mostra o teste padrão da onda produzido combinando as 
primeiras duas ilustrações.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Un terzo di tre illustrazioni che mostrano le 
vibrazioni di una stringa colta del guitar. Questa illustrazione
mostra il modello dell'onda prodotto unendo le prime due 
illustrazioni.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Τρίτο τριών απεικονίσεων που εμφανίζουν τις δονήσεις 
μιας μαδημένης συμβολοσειράς κιθάρων. Αυτή η απεικόνιση 
εμφανίζει πρότυπο κυμάτων που παράγεται με το συνδυασμό των 
πρώτων δύο απεικονίσεων.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Tercero de tres ilustraciones que muestran las 
vibraciones de una cadena desplumada de la guitarra. Esta 
ilustración muestra el modelo de la onda producido combinando las 
primeras dos ilustraciones.</string>
          </description>
